comments.body: We're currently in the final stages of development and testing for our blockchain network. The date for our mainnet launch will be announced shortly. In preparation, mining pool administrators are invited to direct message us for assistance in setting up their nodes in advance of the launch.

comments.author: PowChain
comments.body: The PowChain launch has experienced a delay, but we're moving forward with the event. Are you looking forward to the launch? Share your excitement with us!
